{"tid":2463944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB 記招 有藝人扮姜濤 被指要打到佢變姜蓉  網民：低質、老土又肉酸","createTime":"2021-03-27T05:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T06:27:34.000Z","uid":22556,"like":40,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"e69caa563e5e04602a2ed758508378710a17b4cf","tid":2463944,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:49:34.000Z","msg":"日前（24日）更隆重其事，出動全台多位藝員舉行記者會，介紹即將推出的綜藝節目。<br />\n<br />\n介紹還介紹，推介還推介，可是，一直標榜要開放平台，支持樂壇的TVB，卻竟然容不下一個姜濤？在記者會上，藝人鄧智堅笠了一頭金髮，自稱「薑蓉」，被司儀介紹為「假歌手」的他，在鏡頭前裝模作樣，邊跳邊唱出姜濤的飲歌《蒙著嘴說愛你》歌詞「So I say I love you」，以及「姜B餐」急口令，更做出姜濤的招牌「畀心」手勢，麥美恩見狀，即追打「薑蓉」並大嗌：「收聲啦！」而馮盈盈則尖叫說：「你夠膽嚟踩場？」之後更「護主」話：「打到你變薑蓉！」Bob亦附和大叫：「o趙佢！打佢！」此時，麥美恩即衝出去大力推走鄧智堅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210327/35YBFSMCYVDKNOMWUPZ4RPILVU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3MDa2WGtDOLb90XUyiulObUrj5d1w4-qCFsSR_kQpXY2evtJKqxwBH0rA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210327%2F35YBFSMCYVDKNOMWUPZ4RPILVU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3MDa2WGtDOLb90XUyiulObUrj5d1w4-qCFsSR_kQpXY2evtJKqxwBH0rA&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWiHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=728c4bf6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210327%2F35YBFSMCYVDKNOMWUPZ4RPILVU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3MDa2WGtDOLb90XUyiulObUrj5d1w4-qCFsSR_kQpXY2evtJKqxwBH0rA&h=9692a92f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210327/35YBFSMCYVDKNOMWUPZ4RPILVU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3MDa2WGtDOLb90XUyiulObUrj5d1w4-qCFsSR_kQpXY2evtJK